C. Performance/Profiler
Concept: Flamegraphs for request handling. (Requires V8 hooks/debugger?)
Implementation: We can visualize the middleware stack as a flamegraph. Integrating deeply with V8's CPU profiler is possible but complex; however, a "Logical Flamegraph" of your middleware/handlers is very doable and often more useful.

Implement a schema validator for request payloads in the Network tab and the API Explorer tab. (stretch, this is arbitrary otherwise)

Update the Application graph and use heatmap colors in conjunction with the tooltips to show the hot-paths. (requests, errors, latency, etc.)

Create permission matrix view -- showing request methods+paths and roles required for each path


